{"type": "article", "id": 28277, "title": "扬声器", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-16T06:40:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702153201QEPpOSF1ZrLymJz0.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>如果你喜欢小而精致的桌面音响，不妨来看看 EMIE 推出的这款 Solo One。木质的外壳被设计成留声机的造型，配以 CNC 雕琢一体成型的铝合金底座支撑，整体线条流畅优雅。它在操作上也设计得非常简洁，彻底抛弃了按键，采用的是触摸和滑动进行交互，让人可以更好地感受到实木的触感。这是它的<a href=\"http://cn.emie.com/product/solo_one.html\">购买链接</a>，售价为 699 元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153157bWuc15sQFxjli9e6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153157Gm5rISQCq7VvUERP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153158UV7FGHNO56gfAKqZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702153159IcgGaNxbhe3FOsX0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}